	<h4 class="c-issue-toc__article-title" id="1318"><a href="/en/archive/2013/2-images-of-terror-visibility-of-history/an-archival-impulse-the-return-of-1970s-leftwing-terrorism">An Archival Impulse: The Return of 1970s Leftwing Terrorism in Contemporary German Art.</a></h4>
	<h5 class="c-issue-toc__article-authors"><!--Author:--><a href="/en/bio?id=1260">Svea Bräunert</a></h5>
	
				<a class="c-issue-toc__article-collapse-btn" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseDoi1318" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseSummary1318" data-lexicon-show="show" data-lexicon-hide="hide">
					citation
