</li><li class="c-issue-toc__article c-issue-toc__article--no-translation" data-aricle-no="01">
	<h4 class="c-issue-toc__article-title" id="1713"><a href="/pl/archiwum/2013/2-obrazy-terroru-widzialnosc-historii/terror-i-pamiec">Terror and Memory</a></h4>
